Canonical website:
  https://github.com/libbitcoin/libbitcoin-system

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/libbitcoin/libbitcoin-system/archive/refs/tags/v3.8.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libbitcoin-system-3.8.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libbitcoin-system-3.8.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libbitcoin-system-3.8.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbitcoin-system-3.8.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbitcoin-system0-3.8.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbitcoin-system-devel-3.8.0-X.tar.xz

